    • fillNte

      public static void fillNte(ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.segment.NTE nte, String subject, String fileName, byte[] data) throws ca.uhn.hl7v2.HL7Exception, UnsupportedEncodingException
      Parameters:
      nte -
      subject - should be a short string denoting what's in the comment data, i.e. "REASON_FOR_REFERRAL" or "ALLERGIES", max length is 250
      fileName - should be the file name if applicable, can be null if it didn't come from a file.
      data - and binary data, a String must pass in bytes too as it needs to be base64 encoded for \n and \r's
      Throws:
      ca.uhn.hl7v2.HL7Exception
      UnsupportedEncodingException
